\title{installing [forester](jms-005P)}
\author{jonmsterling}
\date{2023-08-13}

\p{Once you have met the [system requirements](jms-0065), installing [forester](jms-005P) requires only a single shell command:}

\pre{\startverb%
$ opam install forester
\stopverb}

\p{To verify that [forester](jms-005P) is installed, please run \code{forester --version} in your shell.}
